00:47:16.310 --> 00:47:19.440
Since I have a desk job,

00:47:19.910 --> 00:47:21.780
- my back's been aching right here. - Your back? It hurts right here?

00:47:21.840 --> 00:47:22.840
That's the spot.

00:47:23.510 --> 00:47:25.280
- Right here? - Gosh, that feels good.

00:47:25.510 --> 00:47:27.119
- But if it hurts, - That's so relieving.

