I've always wanted to do this.

00:49:59.500 --> 00:50:00.500
Do what?

00:50:03.240 --> 00:50:05.370
- What? - Honey, be home early.

00:50:08.110 --> 00:50:11.750
What was that? That makes us sound like newlyweds.

00:50:13.480 --> 00:50:16.750
But that suit is so dated. Is this the only one you own?

00:50:18.150 --> 00:50:20.490
It's not like I have many chances to wear a suit.

00:50:21.620 --> 00:50:24.060
It just goes to show how I've been living.

00:50:24.260 --> 00:50:27.730
If I win the prize money, I'll get you a tie.

00:50:28.430 --> 00:50:33.070
No, I'll buy you a whole new suit. A designer one.

00:50:33.600 --> 00:50:36.570
You're just saying that because you don't expect to win?

00:50:38.340 --> 00:50:41.540
Once I'm a novelist and you're a professor,

00:50:42.580 --> 00:50:43.680
should we get married?

00:50:44.580 --> 00:50:47.720
Stop it. That's so embarrassing. Seriously, don't.

00:50:48.050 --> 00:50:50.190
Do a good job, hubby.

00:50:50.620 --> 00:50:53.050
- Okay. You got this. - Sure.

00:50:54.490 --> 00:50:57.089
- I'll call you. - Okay, you got this!

00:50:57.090 --> 00:50:58.090
Bye.

