- Your thesis passed. - Yes.

00:52:09.700 --> 00:52:13.400
- Six more credits and you graduate? - Yes, that's correct.

00:52:14.200 --> 00:52:16.670
So why are your undergraduate grades such a mess?

00:52:20.210 --> 00:52:23.950
I was dealing with personal issues at the time.

00:52:24.510 --> 00:52:25.510
Like what?

00:52:28.420 --> 00:52:31.290
- Not that I'm actually asking. - Right.

00:52:31.720 --> 00:52:34.320
Professor Song did recommend you,

