It's not about your timing or even your timing as a couple.

00:54:00.980 --> 00:54:02.980
It's all about her timing.

00:54:04.450 --> 00:54:06.150
How are you supposed to know that?

00:54:06.750 --> 00:54:07.980
That's what makes it so difficult.

