Better yet, just quit your classes and hang out with me all the time.

00:54:33.510 --> 00:54:35.780
How could I not go to my classes?

00:54:36.880 --> 00:54:40.220
Mom, you're really so different from other moms.

00:54:40.720 --> 00:54:43.720
So you wish I were like the other moms?

00:54:44.850 --> 00:54:46.860
No, I'd hate that.

00:54:50.330 --> 00:54:51.330
But...

00:54:53.330 --> 00:54:54.960
aren't you going to find a boyfriend?

