No reason.

00:55:01.870 --> 00:55:02.870
I was just wondering.

00:55:03.610 --> 00:55:05.510
Well, Dad has a girlfriend now.

00:55:05.910 --> 00:55:08.340
I thought you hated the idea of me dating.

00:55:08.480 --> 00:55:11.749
You said you didn't want a new guy, just me, Dad, and you.

00:55:11.750 --> 00:55:14.080
You wanted it to be just you, Dad, and me.

00:55:14.280 --> 00:55:16.890
That was ages ago. I was just a kid.

00:55:17.320 --> 00:55:18.390
And now?

00:55:19.390 --> 00:55:21.760
So now you'd be okay with me having a boyfriend?

00:55:23.360 --> 00:55:24.390
I just...

00:55:27.130 --> 00:55:28.730
I just don't want you to be lonely.

00:55:32.330 --> 00:55:33.800
Do I seem lonely to you?

00:55:37.410 --> 00:55:38.410
I mean...

00:55:40.210 --> 00:55:41.210
Maybe a little?

00:55:45.380 --> 00:55:48.620
Okay. I'll do my best not to be lonely, then.

